and once again, it's a dream...

948
01:12:11,760 --> 01:12:14,130
But I was hoping that I might become...

949
01:12:14,280 --> 01:12:16,170
A bandar-log myself.

950
01:12:16,800 --> 01:12:18,250
Gosh, I wanna be like you.

951
01:12:18,760 --> 01:12:20,440
I am hitching my wagon to your star.

952
01:12:25,640 --> 01:12:26,720
No one leaves!

953
01:12:27,120 --> 01:12:29,280
