954
01:12:47,000 --> 01:12:48,970
We'll try to hold them off.

955
01:13:24,320 --> 01:13:26,000
Where you going, man-cub?

956
01:13:26,400 --> 01:13:28,000
Stay away from me!

957
01:13:28,360 --> 01:13:30,520
You don't have anyone now.

958
01:13:30,680 --> 01:13:33,920
I'm your only hope.
I can make it real good for you here.

959
01:13:34,080 --> 01:13:35,490
Where else you gonna go?

960
01:13:35,960 --> 01:13:37,330
I'll go back to the pack!

961
01:13:37,760 --> 01:13:39,170
I'll go back to akela!

962
01:13:39,840 --> 01:13:41,050
Akela?

963
01:13:41,200 --> 01:13:42,610
Oh.

964
01:13:42,760 --> 01:13:43,970
You didn't hear?

965
01:13:45,840 --> 01:13:47,840
Shere Khan killed him.

966
01:13:50,160 --> 01:13:52,370
Must've been on account of you.

967
01:13:53,040 --> 01:13:54,610
No! You're lying!

968
01:13:59,960 --> 01:14:01,800
Don't run away...

969
01:14:04,800 --> 01:14:07,040
From who you are!
You hear me?

970
01:14:33,880 --> 01:14:36,040
Think about it, man-cub.

971
01:14:39,440 --> 01:14:41,840
We can rule this jungle.

972
01:14:44,680 --> 01:14:45,680
No...

973
01:14:45,760 --> 01:14:47,050
Listen to reason.

974
01:15:03,360 --> 01:15:04,650
Gotcha!

975
01:15:46,840 --> 01:15:48,050
Mowgli!

976
01:16:12,800 --> 01:16:14,610
If anything happens to that kid...

977
01:16:15,080 --> 01:16:16,530
I'll never forgive myself.

978
01:16:17,080 --> 01:16:19,450
- Bagheera!
- Mowgli?

979
01:16:20,760 --> 01:16:21,760
Stay there.

980
01:16:22,160 --> 01:16:23,920
We'll come around to you.

981
01:16:25,680 --> 01:16:27,210
Is it true?

982
01:16:27,680 --> 01:16:28,760
What?

983
01:16:29,240 --> 01:16:31,320
Is akela dead?

984
01:16:32,560 --> 01:16:34,010
We were going to tell you.

985
01:16:35,360 --> 01:16:36,490
You knew!

986
01:16:36,640 --> 01:16:38,170
You both knew!

987
01:16:38,600 --> 01:16:40,890
And nobody did anything about it!

988
01:16:41,040 --> 01:16:42,370
Kid, just hold on.

989
01:16:42,840 --> 01:16:45,210
