993
01:19:23,640 --> 01:19:24,640
Come on!

994
01:19:46,680 --> 01:19:47,890
It's man.

995
01:19:48,040 --> 01:19:49,370
He's come to the jungle.

996
01:19:55,320 --> 01:19:56,920
