997
01:19:57,680 --> 01:19:59,090
The red flower.

998
01:19:59,240 --> 01:20:01,400
Everybody, get to the river!

999
01:20:15,440 --> 01:20:17,570
Red flower.

1000
01:20:18,560 --> 01:20:20,560
Pups, come on. Stay close.

1001
01:20:34,760 --> 01:20:37,130
Is that Mowgli?

1002
01:20:40,360 --> 01:20:41,810
Shere Khan!

1003
01:20:43,480 --> 01:20:44,720
Shere Khan!

1004
01:20:44,880 --> 01:20:46,250
I'm not afraid of you!

1005
01:20:46,440 --> 01:20:48,680
No one has to be afraid of you any more!

1006
01:20:53,280 --> 01:20:54,330
No...

1007
01:20:57,880 --> 01:21:01,200
I think they're afraid
of something else now.

1008
01:21:17,040 --> 01:21:19,280
The man-cub is now a man.

1009
01:21:22,520 --> 01:21:23,520
Gray...

1010
01:21:27,520 --> 01:21:29,200
Always a proud day...

1011
