When they come of age.

1012
01:21:34,840 --> 01:21:38,640
You can fool them, but you can't fool me.

1013
01:21:39,440 --> 01:21:42,330
I'm the one who saw your future.

1014
01:21:43,000 --> 01:21:45,530
I saw what you'd become.

1015
